Glencore Confirms Plan to Raise as Much as $11 Billion in Initial Offering

-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-04-14T06:01:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/glencore-confirms-plan-to-raise-as-much-as-11-billion-in-initial-offering.html
Glencore International AG, the
Swiss commodities trader, confirmed it plans to sell as much as
$11 billion in shares in an initial public offering in  London 
and  Hong Kong .  The Baar, Switzerland-based company commented in a
regulatory statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Amanda Jordan in London at 
